\begin_inset Formula $n=1,2,\dotsc,\infty$
\end_inset

.)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
For 
\begin_inset Formula $X,Y$
\end_inset

 by Kunneth we have 
\begin_inset Formula $K\left(p,n-1\right)_{*}\left(X\otimes Y\right)=K\left(p,n-1\right)_{*}\left(X\right)\otimes K\left(p,n-1\right)_{*}\left(Y\right)$
