\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{Spc}\left(\mathrm{Sp}_{\left(p\right)}^{\mathrm{fin}}\right)=\left\{ \mathcal{C}_{\geq1},\mathcal{C}_{\geq2},\dotsc,\mathcal{C}_{\geq\infty}\right\} $
\end_inset

